The python script needs a virtual environment with Selenium installed on the system.

General Steps:

1. Download and copy selenium to root directory.
2. Create and load the virtual environment. Install dependencies (selenium).
3. Run the python script - tinder_bot.py

The application will open a chrome browser, log in using Facebook/any other specified credentials and start swiping till it meets a popup, in which case it will switch back to the main screen and continue swiping.

